<topic template="Default" modified="2026-03-09T12:22:27.611Z" lasteditedby="noorhbo" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>轴行程限制</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading3">轴行程限制</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">轴参照位置</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">过行程</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50;">每个轴的行程受 NC 软件限值（软 OT1）的限制。</para>
    <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50; font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">软 OT1</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal">如果为某轴发送的命令超出其行程极限，NC 设备将停止该轴的运动。 这种情况会触发警报，但不会导致紧急停止。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><image src="Fig 2.4_Chp 5.png" scale="60.00%" width="492" height="613" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Figure E" style="margin-bottom:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:11pt;">图 &lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER5=2%&gt;.&lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER%&gt; </text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">X 行程限值</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Figure E" style="margin-bottom:0px;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Figure E" style="margin-bottom:0px;"><image src="Fig 2.5_Chp 5.png" scale="60.00%" width="485" height="290" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Figure E" style="margin-bottom:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:11pt;">图 &lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER5=2%&gt;.&lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER%&gt; </text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">Y 冲程限制</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Figure E" style="margin-bottom:0px;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Figure E" style="margin-bottom:0px;"><image src="Fig 2.6_Chp 5.png" scale="60.00%" width="486" height="288" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
